PrecisAuthority to enter into a "SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT" with the PIAPOT BAND OF INDIAN for the purpose of resolving specific claims pertaining to the Surrender for Leasing (grazing) of some 15,360 acres of Piapot Indian Reserve No. 75 in Saskatchewan done on March 20, 1918, as well as the Surrender for Sale of another 2,180 acres of land done on May 28, 1918.
